title: Lizzie Armanto on Tony Hawk's 360 loop, skateboarding, and the Olympics
description: Skater Lizzie Armanto is the first woman to complete Tony Hawk's incredible 360 loop. She joins the Olympic Channel Podcast to talk Finland, skateboarding, and Sky Brown. Plus, we have the best bits from our Olympic Day workouts. Go to OlympicChannel.com/Podcast for more episodes and to subscribe.
